         = +1\n| timezone_DST            = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset_DST          = +2\n| postal_code_type        = [[List of postal codes in the Netherlands|Postal code]]\n| postal_code             =\n| area_code_type          = [[Telephone numbers in the Netherlands|Dialing code]]\n| area_code               =\n| website                 =\n| footnotes               =\n}}\n'''Reuzenhoek''' is a town in the [[Netherlands|Dutch]] province of [[Zeeland]]. It is a part of the municipality of [[Terneuzen]], and lies about 28&nbsp;km southeast of [[Vlissingen]].\n\nThe statistical area \"Reuzenhoek\", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 150.<ref name=\"CBS2\">Statistics Netherlands (CBS), [http://statline.cbs.nl/ ''Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005'']. As of 1 January 2005.</ref>\n\n==References==\n<!--This article uses the Cite.php citation mechanism. If you would like more information on how to add references to this article, please see http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Cite/Cite.php -->\n<references/>\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Zeeland]]\n[[Category:Terneuzen]]\n\n\n{{Zeeland-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Reuzenhoek\n| settlement_type         = Town\n| other_name              = <!-- if different from name -->\n| native_name             = <!-- if different from name -->\n| native_name_lang        = nl\n| image_skyline           =\n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           =\n| image_flag              =\n| image_shield            =\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n| image_map               = LocatieTerneuzen.png\n| map_caption             =\n| image_map1              = Map NL - Terneuzen - Reuzenhoek.png\n| map_caption1            = Reuzenhoek in the municipality of Terneuzen.\n| pushpin_map             = <!-- Netherlands -->\n| pushpin_